    "Choose Celsius or Fahrenheit, and 12-hour or 24-hour time — or let the system decide." : {
      "comment" : "What's New 1.3 — temperature & time format feature subtitle.",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
